- Sales trend analysis
- Product performance analysis
- Store performance comparison
- Interactive reporting using slicers

---

## How to Use
1. Download the Excel file from this repository
2. Open it in Microsoft Excel
3. Go to the dashboard sheet
4. Use the **Month** and **Day** slicers to interact with the report
5. Analyze KPIs and charts for business insights

---

## Conclusion
This Excel dashboard project demonstrates how raw sales data can be transformed into an interactive and insightful business report. It is useful for beginners and aspiring data analysts who want to strengthen their Excel dashboarding and business analysis skills.

